data.description: This home is located on a nice corner lot, close to Crossett Elementary School and park with exercise equipment inside park. Home features Three bedroom and two bathrooms, large living room with freshly painted built ins and whitewashed fireplace, Large Formal Dining Room and spacious kitchen. Great cabinets with a huge wooden island. Gas stainless steel stove, new backsplash, and dishwasher. You also have a eat in breakfast area. So much space to entertain and spread out! The downstairs bathroom has been remodeled, new light fixtures added through out home, and new flooring added.  The master suite is located upstairs. The bathroom has been updated and a new closet has been added (making it two closets!) Seller has Window Unit and standing heater for this master. Very spacious and a private patio off the master bedroom. Privacy and chain link fenced in the back yard. Nice size yard with shade trees for your family. Workshop area under the carport.  This home is move-in ready and is waiting for you and your family.
